Some useful introductory information about Google Analytics.I wasn't able to connect with the demo account through Rhyme. This was kinda frustrating, and I ended up logging in to my actual account via browser and outside Rhyme. The Rhyme platform for Guided Projects is nice, but adds little or no value as long as you have to login with your true credentials and work on a live application that is already available with a normal browser access. In this context any good YouTube video on the topic would do the same job (except the final quiz, that is not on Rhyme anyway).

Good course for the fundamentals of Google Analytics including how to set an account, link your website and understanding the analytics report. Would give 5 stars if this covered the most current version of Google Analytics.
